OL,3,CArmy veteran thanks organ donor's
OL,4,Cfamily for giving him 'reason to live'
OL,6,FAdrienne's husband and daughter say
OL,7,Fthey are both incredibly proud after
OL,8,Freading the letter.
OL,10,FPaul Fry, Adrienne's husband, said:
OL,11,F"It's very emotional because suddenly
OL,12,Fyou have a connection between the
OL,13,Fperson you've lost and somebody who is
OL,14,Fbenefiting from that loss, which is
OL,15,Fquite a unique experience.
OL,17,F"And it also gives the family solace
OL,18,Fto know that there is something
OL,19,Fpositive coming out of that awful
OL,20,Fexperience of death, which we all will
OL,21,Fgo through."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
