OL,3,CArmy veteran thanks organ donor's
OL,4,Cfamily for giving him 'reason to live'
OL,6,FAmanda Gaunt, Adrienne's daughter,
OL,7,Fsaid: "When we went to see her after
OL,8,Fthe machines were taken off and post
OL,9,Forgan removal, it was really sad and
OL,10,Fwe did try and turn it into a
OL,11,Fpositive, saying that we were stood
OL,12,Fthere crying as a family, but there
OL,13,Fwould be another family crying with
OL,14,Fjoy."
OL,16,FSince 2020 an opt-out system in
OL,17,FEngland was introduced, where there is
OL,18,Fassumed consent for organ donation.
