OL,3,CArmy veteran thanks organ donor's
OL,4,Cfamily for giving him 'reason to live'
OL,6,FBut Paul and Amanda are still urging
OL,7,Fpeople to join the organ donor
OL,8,Fregister and discuss it with their
OL,9,Floved ones.
OL,11,FOrgan donation will not go ahead if
OL,12,Ffamily members object.
OL,14,FThey want more lives might saved, but
OL,15,Falso want to see other families have a
OL,16,Fsimilarly positive experience.
